Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.54,0:00:07.46,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:14.75,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:22.93,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I closed my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:28.94,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and distanced myself from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.95,0:00:35.70,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,5 PM in the school yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:42.58,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,The ball's shadow is growing tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:50.04,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.95,0:00:53.76,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever we meet in the hallway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:58.51,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,we always quarreled.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:06.69,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Halfway through a kiss,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:13.65,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,tears dropped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:20.99,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,Because I opened my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:27.79,song-op,Song,0000,0000,0000,,and we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:40.57,eptitle,title,0000,0350,0000,,Episode 4\N\N\NBargain Typhoon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:05.55,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this a cute dress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:06.48,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.38,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best one recommended for this spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.82,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.27,0:02:20.64,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.30,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,Take a closer look, see this red?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:28.75,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,There's a smooth line along the shoulder and all these frills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:30.84,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't that many other dresses that're this finely made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:32.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:48.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This is great, maybe I should get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.66,Default,tag,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H101360&}56,000 yen.\N(approx. $510.00)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:58.44,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,So, did it fit?  Wow!\NYou look very pretty in it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:00.24,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.50,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,This's the only one in this color.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.01,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,It's all cotton, so it's easy to wash.  A best buy, I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:12.78,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,That's no problem.  Just leave a deposit and we'll hold it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:16.30,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,This's the only one of this color.\NNow, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:18.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.22,0:03:22.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, the frills are cute and the color is wonderful, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.84,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, there's nobody who would look as I would in this dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.24,0:03:31.06,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I love this dress.  Honestly.  I want it badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:31.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:33.94,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I can't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:35.74,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:47.42,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage...Mikage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:49.76,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}MIKAGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.96,0:03:56.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use telepathy like that, Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:59.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Well I tried calling you for a time, but you wouldn't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.24,0:04:00.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:05.16,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I need some help on the math homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.25,0:04:08.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.  I've got something else on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.82,0:04:09.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:13.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  A very highly philosophical one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.  I'll do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:16.76,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:19.25,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:22.66,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cold.  Look how deeply troubled I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you at least ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:32.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.85,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.34,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Whaa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I found a really cute dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.90,0:04:43.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I want it real bad, so can I borrow some money?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:46.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, why don't you ask mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:50.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that.  She just bought me this skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.54,0:04:53.18,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,How much is the dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:57.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,56,000 yen!  It's expensive, but really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:04.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful red and has lots of frills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.50,0:05:05.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:06.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:08.40,Default,TOmomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my homework by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.40,0:05:09.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.62,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.25,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Nice heading!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:31.00,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:34.12,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?  Did you quarrel or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:35.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.90,0:05:39.24,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Ohh, Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:43.78,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair, Noda.  Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel!  I had to get up early to cook all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:49.06,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, what are you ticked off about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:53.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business!  Stupid Noda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:06:03.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,She found a dress she wanted to buy, but it's too expensive for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.55,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,How expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.48,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,56,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:08.00,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.55,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:13.62,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.38,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, there's no need to apologize to that idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:20.84,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.  No need to say sorry to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.38,Default,Male,0000,0000,0000,,Noda?  where's the ball?  What's keeping you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:29.40,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!  See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:33.27,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer the egg a little sweeter.  See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:48.65,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,We're short-handed today, can you work the counter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:51.84,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember what I told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.84,0:06:52.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.51,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,Then, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.06,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:06:58.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:02.54,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,A fish burger, one potato, and a woolong tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.54,0:07:05.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that was a fish burger, one potato, and a woolong tea, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.82,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance are you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.90,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This combination is for that, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.12,0:07:12.62,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:16.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Then, you should forget the potato and take the salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.20,0:07:19.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Potatoes are high in calories, I'll change that to a salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.93,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,No, potato!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:22.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.10,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:25.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be 580 yen.\N(approx. $5.30)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.79,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,We're terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.02,Default,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.80,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.80,0:07:37.00,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,Matsunaga-kun, can you go over to the kitchen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.02,Default,worker,0000,0000,0000,,Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:52.22,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,Now what did she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:58.74,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I was trying to make a special burger, but it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.27,Default,manager,0000,0000,0000,,You're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.98,0:08:11.78,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:15.44,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the dress, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:15.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.12,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,It's very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.92,0:08:23.48,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!  No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:26.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You said yes before.  Now give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.18,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:29.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,But this is the only way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.64,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet.  What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:37.18,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, we'd like to help you on your experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.40,0:08:39.30,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Really, Matsunaga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but here's the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.03,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,50,000 yen?\N(approx. $455.00)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.70,0:08:51.08,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, what are you going to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi will receive these cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.86,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Teleportation?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.20,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:11.80,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,At last, I get to see this.  Now, show me your powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:16.65,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, are you sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:18.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:21.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.70,0:09:26.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.40,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Teleport complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.44,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:49.92,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So, it was teleporta....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:54.58,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,That was only a trick!  Stop fooling around.  Show me your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:55.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.92,Default,Kageura,0000,0000,0000,,Good thing I didn't pay in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:12.25,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:17.74,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting to make it look like I've been harassing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:23.51,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.10,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:33.36,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:37.40,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.42,0:10:43.20,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just looking for you, but I ended up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,So you like that skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:48.40,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but this is expensive too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:50.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, hear this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:56.64,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Then me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.46,Default,M&T,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Comment: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:06.60,Default,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eye Catch
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,And this section should be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:35.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:39.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Bargain strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.16,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Bargain strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:44.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We'll begin training tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.48,0:11:45.04,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:49.38,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I gotta do something about these guys here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the main floor.  There are three entrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go in from the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.00,0:12:00.58,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we just go in from the front?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.24,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,That's the height of folly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.98,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,That's the height of folly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:10.48,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you actually know what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.76,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This side should be less crowded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:15.00,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,{"shiranai"} I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.70,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,The dumbest thing you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:21.00,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Noda, I bet you did well on that essay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.90,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yamagishi-kun, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.51,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Just move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:29.42,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.48,0:12:31.92,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:33.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Stand at that corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.10,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.13,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Is this good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.13,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What's she up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.66,0:12:43.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.62,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage-chan, what brand of shampoo do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.30,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.25,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.72,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,OK.  Now, on the X-day, you will stand here and block everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.32,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What a cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.80,0:12:57.00,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.44,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,And here's the second point, the escalator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:05.74,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,With Noda up front, Tomomi and I will block the way to stop others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.68,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,That's dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.90,0:13:08.68,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Owww.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.42,0:13:12.92,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,And here's the third floor, the main battleground.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:17.18,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as reason here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.20,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take bargains that lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody else is your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:23.20,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:25.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,There's no mercy at bargains.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:26.55,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:32.00,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,To get around this corner first, we'll have Noda get ahead with Tomomi following.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:37.60,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Using Noda as an anchor, Tomomi will cut the corner and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.70,0:13:41.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Goal In!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:48.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What about my skirt?  Hey, Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:12.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, the dress will be mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, knock it off.  You told us to go to sleep early!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:18.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:38.02,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Holy cow.  I guess Mikage's plan won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:41.02,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This was part of the plan from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:43.86,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, do as I told you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.88,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.06,0:15:27.44,Default,Yamagishi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda, look, cute girls all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:38.54,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.22,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:49.88,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:50.62,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:52.36,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:55.98,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, don't step on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.80,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop pushing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:01.20,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me, tell that to whoever's behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:04.22,Default,saleslad,0000,0000,0000,,All merchandise is 50 percent off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:06.12,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.36,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:11.38,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.12,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.72,0:16:24.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:24.84,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,ehh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:26.60,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:29.66,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.66,0:16:32.18,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's Yamagishi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.66,0:16:40.46,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.00,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.51,0:16:44.40,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:02.60,Default,woman,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.88,0:17:06.64,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.18,0:17:10.60,Default,Yamagish0,0000,0000,0000,,I was completely surrounded by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:14.60,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.84,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,No...no...I can't find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.38,0:17:26.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:29.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi?...Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:30.86,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.04,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:35.60,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's too scary where you are and I have things I want to buy, also.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:37.75,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.75,0:17:38.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.58,0:17:41.12,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you?  I can't find the dress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.66,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will after I buy this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No.  Come over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:50.30,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:55.34,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:09.58,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.58,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.90,0:18:21.90,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage?...Mikage, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:08.98,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.27,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:26.24,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.32,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:37.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Noda-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:39.34,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:40.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.48,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:48.22,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:52.68,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,You're late.  Where were you?  Give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:54.74,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,But...you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.54,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.25,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:05.50,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage, did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.51,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:09.50,Default,Yamagish,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:11.76,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hold on much longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.88,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Don't rush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:19.16,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:22.55,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:26.54,Default,Noda,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?  You found it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:30.51,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,This collar...  I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:32.50,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,MIKAGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:00.74,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mikage, what was that thing this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:05.70,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was strange, wasn't it?  It could be the bracelets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.00,0:21:08.34,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bracelets?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:16.10,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our power could have become more sensitive because of the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:21.84,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If it did become more sensitive, I wish you had noticed the shape of the collar earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.08,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:25.72,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:51.72,Default,T&M,0000,0000,0000,,Miracle Girls here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.08,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have against me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.10,0:21:55.36,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:57.78,Default,Tomomi,0000,0000,0000,,No way.  Noda-kun saw me in terrible shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:01.51,Default,T&M,0000,0000,0000,,Next on Miracle Girls, "Mostly Mikage, Partially Tomomi."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:04.27,Default,Mikage,0000,0000,0000,,Tomomi, how do you play volleyball?
