Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:08.73,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:12.22,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.30,0:22:15.34,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we had a fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:18.87,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:38.86,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,There are days when kindness is so close that you can't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.22,0:22:50.75,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we know better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.07,0:22:58.86,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,When we can't say "I'm sorry,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.97,0:23:06.44,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we send out feelings through the little fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.57,0:23:12.05,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Going over the tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.84,0:23:15.42,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,we want to be honest to ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:21.21,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause the sky deserves a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:23.72,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever we do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:27.29,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,there has to be both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.25,0:23:30.42,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:34.59,song-ed,song,0000,0000,0000,,are better than one of us.
